en.online: Whether the character is currently online.
en.station_id: Current station ID (0 if not docked).
en.skillqueue_count: Number of skills in the queue.
en.skillqueue_current_level: Training level for the current skill.
en.skillqueue_current_end: Finish time for the current skill (ISO).
en.skillqueue_ends_at: Finish time for the last queued skill (ISO).
en.industry_jobs_total: Total industry jobs returned by ESI.
en.notifications_count: Number of notifications returned by ESI.
